Name: Rounded
About the game: Classic puzzle games are bored, right? How about changing your perception of the puzzle game. A very challenging and fun adventure awaits you. No need to say too much, everyone deserves it! MANY DIFFERENT LOCATIONS The joy of solving mazes in dozens of unique places. You will feel like you are there! ATTRACTIVE GRAPHICS How would you like to have an experience with great graphics? FOR THOSE WHO LOVE DIFFICULT Character control, labyrinth design and obstacles. It adds you a difficult game with everything. TWO DIFFERENT MODES How would you like to try the hard levels that are almost impossible to pass, except for the classic episodes? With everything, a completely different game awaits you.
